<h1><font color="#5C8526">Milestone : Algorithm of Problem 1</font></h1>
<ul><li><h2>To calculate minimal cover G for F</h2></li>
<li><h2>1. Set G := F</h2></li>
<li><h2>2. Replace each functional dependency X --&gt; {A1,A2, ..., Ak} in G by the k functional dependencies X --&gt; A1, X --&gt; A2, ... X-&gt; Ak</h2></li>
<li><h2>3. For each functional dependency X --&gt; A in G</h2></li>
<li><h2>    for each attribute B that is an element of X</h2></li>
<li><h2>        if ((G - {X --&gt; A}) U {(X - {B} -&gt; A)}) is equivalent to G</h2></li>
<li><h2>            then replace X --&gt; A with (X - {B}) -&gt; A in G</h2></li>
<li><h2>4. For each remaining functional dependency X --&gt; A in G</h2></li>
<li><h2>        if (G - {X --&gt; A}) is equivalent to G</h2></li>
<li><h2>            then remove X --&gt; A from G.</h2></li>
</ul></body>
